This program will find each instance of a specified string of characters in a file and replace them with another specied string.

BEFORE you use:: 

The file that you are going to be searching must be in the same folder as the program executable, 
make sure you take note of file types or extentions as these must be included in the file name.

INSTRUCTIONS::

	run the program (it will open in a terminal window)

	when prompted enter the name of the file to edit

	when prompted enter the string to find

	when prompted enter the string to insert

close terminal


